      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Engines</a> * Chessterfield</b>\n</p><p><b>Chessterfield</b>,<br />\na family of chess engines by <a href=\"/Matthias_L%C3%BCscher\" title=\"Matthias Lüscher\">Matthias Lüscher</a>, written in <a href=\"/Cpp\" title=\"Cpp\">C++</a>, first released in April 1998. The free native Chessterfield comes with an own <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a>, the experimental <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a> compliant ChessterfieldCL along with its <a href=\"/Learning\" title=\"Learning\">learning utility</a> ChessterfieldEN is <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source</a> published under the  <a href=\"/Free_Software_Foundation#GPL\" title=\"Free Software Foundation\">GNU General Public Licence V2</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>. Chessterfield applies <a href=\"/Alpha-Beta\" title=\"Alpha-Beta\">alpha-beta</a> with <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">transposition table</a>, <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">null move pruning</a>, <a href=\"/Razoring\" title=\"Razoring\">razoring</a> and various <a href=\"/Extensions\" title=\"Extensions\">extensions</a> inside an <a href=\"/Aspiration_Windows\" title=\"Aspiration Windows\">aspirated</a> <a href=\"/Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Iterative Deepening\">iterative deepening</a> loop. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Screenshot\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Screenshot</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#ChessterfieldCL\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">ChessterfieldCL</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Chess_Engine\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Engine</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Chesterfield\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chesterfield</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Screenshot\">Screenshot</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chessterfield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Screenshot\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"http://home.datacomm.ch/m.luescher/screenshot.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"ChessterfieldGUImansfield.gif\" src=\"/images/a/af/ChessterfieldGUImansfield.gif\" width=\"548\" height=\"454\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div> \n<p>Chessterfield <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"ChessterfieldCL\">ChessterfieldCL</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chessterfield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: ChessterfieldCL\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>While affiliated with <a href=\"/ETH_Zurich\" title=\"ETH Zurich\">ETH Zurich</a>, inspired by <a href=\"/Michael_Buro\" title=\"Michael Buro\">Michael Buro's</a> <a href=\"/CG_1998\" title=\"CG 1998\">CG 1998</a> paper <i>From Simple Features to Sophisticated Evaluation Functions</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>, covering not only <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">automated parameter tuning</a> but a procedure for exploring the feature space able to discover new features in a computational feasible way, Matthias Lüscher implemented Buro's <a href=\"/Michael_Buro#GLEM\" title=\"Michael Buro\">General Linear Evaluation Model (GLEM)</a> inside <b>ChessterfieldCL</b>, using a three-layer <a href=\"/Neural_Networks\" title=\"Neural Networks\">neural network</a> as <a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">evaluation function</a> - documented in his technical report under supervision of <a href=\"/Thomas_Lincke\" title=\"Thomas Lincke\">Thomas Lincke</a> and <a href=\"/Christoph_Wirth\" title=\"Christoph Wirth\">Christoph Wirth</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>. Christoph Wirth's <a href=\"/Endgame_Tablebases\" title=\"Endgame Tablebases\">endgame tablebases</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> were used to verify the effectiveness of the trained evaluation function in particular endgames <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chessterfield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Neural_Networks#engines\" title=\"Neural Networks\">Chess Engines with Neural Networks</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Chester\" title=\"Chester\">Chester</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Publications\">Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chessterfield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Matthias_L%C3%BCscher\" title=\"Matthias Lüscher\">Matthias Lüscher</a>  (<b>2000</b>). <i>Automatic Generation of an Evaluation Function for Chess Endgames</i>. <a href=\"/ETH_Zurich\" title=\"ETH Zurich\">ETH Zurich</a> Supervisors: <a href=\"/Thomas_Lincke\" title=\"Thomas Lincke\">Thomas Lincke</a> and <a href=\"/Christoph_Wirth\" title=\"Christoph Wirth\">Christoph Wirth</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.datacomm.ch/m.luescher/evaluation_function_en.pdf\">pdf</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chessterfield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=31189\">ChessterfieldCL stürzt ständig ab</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Clemens_Keck&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Clemens Keck (page does not exist)\">Clemens Keck</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, March 24, 2000 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/rec.games.chess.computer/xthKCFRJkeM/CwRxa1j7Q1IJ\">Combining Neural Networks and Alpha-Beta</a> by <a href=\"/Matthias_L%C3%BCscher\" title=\"Matthias Lüscher\">Matthias Lüscher</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, April 01, 2000</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/rec.games.chess.computer/sdfJVjnz_MA/cg-ibeL_4HYJ\">Learning utility for Chessterfield available</a> by <a href=\"/Matthias_L%C3%BCscher\" title=\"Matthias Lüscher\">Matthias Lüscher</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, May 29, 2001</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=149124\">Chessterfield Source Code Available</a> by <a href=\"/Matthias_L%C3%BCscher\" title=\"Matthias Lüscher\">Matthias Lüscher</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 10, 2001</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://kirill-kryukov.com/chess/discussion-board/viewtopic.php?f=6&amp;t=2923\">Chris Wirth's endgame tablebases</a> by <a href=\"/Denis_Mendoza\" title=\"Denis Mendoza\">Denis P. Mendoza</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">CCRL Endgame Tablebases</a>, December 13, 2007</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chessterfield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess_Engine\">Chess Engine</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chessterfield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: Chess Engine\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://home.datacomm.ch/m.luescher/index.html\">Chessterfield Chess Program</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://home.datacomm.ch/m.luescher/download_cl.html\">ChessterfieldCL Download</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://kirill-kryukov.com/chess/kcec/cgi/engine_details.cgi?print=Details&amp;each_game=1&amp;eng=ChessterfieldCL%20i5a%20JA\">ChessterfieldCL i5a JA</a> in <a href=\"/KCEC\" title=\"KCEC\">KCEC</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chesterfield\">Chesterfield</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chessterfield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: Chesterfield\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/chesterfield\">chesterfield - Wiktionary</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chesterfield_%28disambiguation%29\">Chesterfield (disambiguation) from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chesterfield\">Chesterfield from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://chesterfieldchessclub.weebly.com/\">Chesterfield Chess Club</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chesterfield_%28cigarette%29\">Chesterfield (cigarette) from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cancerinsurance.com/blog/smoking-and-cancer-film-stars-who-died-of-cancer\">Smoking and Cancer: Classic Film Stars Who Died of Cancer</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chesterfield_coat\">Chesterfield coat from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chesterfield_County,_South_Carolina\">Chesterfield County, South Carolina from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chesterfield_County,_Virginia\">Chesterfield County, Virginia from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Couch\">Chesterfield sofa from Wikipedia</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chessterfield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://home.datacomm.ch/m.luescher/download_cl.html\">ChessterfieldCL Download</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://home.datacomm.ch/m.luescher/screenshot.html\">Chessterfield GUI screenshot</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Michael_Buro\" title=\"Michael Buro\">Michael Buro</a> (<b>1998</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/3-540-48957-6_8\">From Simple Features to Sophisticated Evaluation Functions</a></i>. <a href=\"/CG_1998\" title=\"CG 1998\">CG 1998</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://skatgame.net/mburo/ps/glem.pdf\">pdf</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-b